- Definitely.

764
01:04:28,148 --> 01:04:30,067
Hey, good looking. How are you?

765
01:04:30,192 --> 01:04:31,693
Good. This is cool.

766
01:04:31,777 --> 01:04:34,780
- I just got it. You want a ride?
- Some other time.

767
01:04:35,030 --> 01:04:38,033
- Are you sure?
