Small board, left hand.
Big board, right hand.

847
01:11:37,828 --> 01:11:41,331
- I'm almost done.
- All of fence.

848
01:11:45,460 --> 01:11:50,299
Big board, right hand.
Small board, left hand.

849
01:11:50,716 --> 01:11:52,676
Up, down.

850
01:11:53,719 --> 01:11:55,804
Up, down.

