Encino Oaks Country Club. 9:30.

937
01:21:54,361 --> 01:21:57,030
Friday? Great.

938
01:21:57,155 --> 01:21:59,616
- Hi, Ali.
- "Hi, Ali."

939
01:21:59,700 --> 01:22:01,743
I've got to be nuts.

940
